{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"300","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/resources/layout,_N_T_/resources/soc-reports/layout,_N_T_/resources/soc-reports/page,_N_T_/resources/soc-reports"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><!--p3FRDNbUcHiyXkEKEwNIa--><html lang=\"en\" class=\"__variable_f79d48 __variable_88a864\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/10031fe4fe41fe1d-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/60c43daa125debce-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"preload\" href=\"/_next/static/media/d6c9cc715edbd740-s.p.woff2\" as=\"font\" crossorigin=\"\" type=\"font/woff2\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/e940280de3e4a05c.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-0cc30f5d22cae38b.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/56a3b17b-e05b7ee33c2fd907.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/954-652db48e153037a0.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-40ff7d9a18fe3d9a.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/814-9c5994eabc7467f2.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/layout-3bfa2e48ad2203b4.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/201-563e3800e322e1bb.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/64-6b869f8fe5c65808.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/resources/soc-reports/page-b06dd1295dd2ecd2.js\" async=\"\"></script><meta name=\"next-size-adjust\" content=\"\"/><title>Altimi Tech Due Diligence</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"Independent technology assessment for investors. Surface hidden risks, validate scalability, and make confident decisions.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico\" type=\"image/jpeg\"/><link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/apple-touch-icon.jpg\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><nav class=\"sticky top-0 z-[999] bg-[#0a1926]\"><div class=\"max-w-[1540px] mx-auto flex items-center justify-between h-[64px] px-[105px] max-md:px-6\"><a class=\"shrink-0\" href=\"/\"><img alt=\"Altimi\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"112\" height=\"28\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-7 w-auto\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-altimi-white.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-altimi-white.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-altimi-white.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/></a><a class=\"font-mono text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.65px] text-white/90 hover:text-white transition-colors\" href=\"/\">← Back to home</a></div></nav><main class=\"bg-white\"><div class=\"max-w-[800px] mx-auto px-[105px] max-md:px-6 py-[80px] max-md:py-[40px]\"><span class=\"inline-block font-mono text-[13px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.65px] text-[#0a1926]/70 bg-[#0a1926]/8 px-4 py-1.5 rounded mb-6\">Research · 485 companies · $291M+ tracked</span><h1 class=\"text-[#0a1926] text-[clamp(32px,5vw,48px)] leading-[1.1] font-normal mb-6\">500 SOC 2 Reports. One Uncomfortable Truth.</h1><p class=\"text-[#333333] text-[18px] leading-[1.6] mb-12\">We analyzed every page of 485 compliance reports from companies backed by a16z, Benchmark, Kleiner Perkins, Lightspeed, and Y Combinator. The finding: compliance does not equal maturity.</p><div class=\"grid grid-cols-5 max-md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 mb-16\"><div class=\"border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]\">485</div><div class=\"text-[12px] text-[#333333] mt-1\">companies analyzed</div></div><div class=\"border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]\">99%</div><div class=\"text-[12px] text-[#333333] mt-1\">have MFA</div></div><div class=\"border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]\">28%</div><div class=\"text-[12px] text-[#333333] mt-1\">multi-region</div></div><div class=\"border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]\">22%</div><div class=\"text-[12px] text-[#333333] mt-1\">cyber insured</div></div><div class=\"border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-4 text-center\"><div class=\"text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]\">70%</div><div class=\"text-[12px] text-[#333333] mt-1\">template boilerplate</div></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4 mb-16\"><div class=\"flex gap-4 items-start border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-5\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]/30 shrink-0 w-10\">01</span><div><p class=\"text-[#0a1926] text-[16px] font-medium mb-1\">$75M buys you the same SOC 2 as $500K.</p><p class=\"text-[#333333] text-[15px] leading-[1.6]\">Across 27 researched companies ($291M total), funding level has zero correlation with compliance quality.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 items-start border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-5\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]/30 shrink-0 w-10\">02</span><div><p class=\"text-[#0a1926] text-[16px] font-medium mb-1\">70% of every report is copy-paste.</p><p class=\"text-[#333333] text-[15px] leading-[1.6]\">One auditor. Same template. Identical control descriptions across hundreds of companies.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 items-start border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-5\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]/30 shrink-0 w-10\">03</span><div><p class=\"text-[#0a1926] text-[16px] font-medium mb-1\">78% pass SOC 2 without cyber insurance.</p><p class=\"text-[#333333] text-[15px] leading-[1.6]\">If they trusted their security controls, cyber insurance would be cheap and obvious. Its absence says more than the audit opinion.</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 items-start border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-5\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]/30 shrink-0 w-10\">04</span><div><p class=\"text-[#0a1926] text-[16px] font-medium mb-1\">100% have a disaster recovery plan. 49% never tested it.</p><p class=\"text-[#333333] text-[15px] leading-[1.6]\">The gap between policy and practice is the real story. SOC 2 counts both as &#x27;available.&#x27;</p></div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 items-start border border-[#0a1926]/10 rounded-xl p-5\"><span class=\"font-mono text-[24px] font-medium text-[#0a1926]/30 shrink-0 w-10\">05</span><div><p class=\"text-[#0a1926] text-[16px] font-medium mb-1\">SOC 2 tells you nothing about what actually matters.</p><p class=\"text-[#333333] text-[15px] leading-[1.6]\">Code quality. SDLC process. Team capability. Tech debt. AI practices. Zero signal in 500 reports.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"border-t border-[#0a1926]/10 my-16\"></div><div class=\"border-2 border-[#0a1926] rounded-2xl p-10 max-md:p-6 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-[28px] font-normal text-[#0a1926] mb-4\">Download the full report</h2><p class=\"text-[#333333] text-[16px] leading-[1.6] mb-8 max-w-[500px] mx-auto\">7 sections, 12 charts, 4,000 words. Everything SOC 2 reveals — and everything it hides — backed by data from 485 companies.</p><form class=\"max-w-[400px] mx-auto space-y-3\"><input type=\"email\" required=\"\" placeholder=\"Work email\" class=\"w-full h-[48px] px-4 rounded-[6.5px] border border-[#0a1926]/15 text-[16px] text-[#0a1926] placeholder:text-[#0a1926]/40 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#0a1926]/40\" value=\"\"/><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Name (optional)\" class=\"w-full h-[48px] px-4 rounded-[6.5px] border border-[#0a1926]/15 text-[16px] text-[#0a1926] placeholder:text-[#0a1926]/40 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#0a1926]/40\" value=\"\"/><input type=\"text\" placeholder=\"Company (optional)\" class=\"w-full h-[48px] px-4 rounded-[6.5px] border border-[#0a1926]/15 text-[16px] text-[#0a1926] placeholder:text-[#0a1926]/40 focus:outline-none focus:border-[#0a1926]/40\" value=\"\"/><button type=\"submit\" class=\"w-full font-mono text-[15px] font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.65px] bg-[#0a1926] text-white h-[52px] rounded-[6.5px] flex items-center justify-center hover:bg-[#0a1926]/90 transition-colors disabled:opacity-50\">Get the report</button></form><p class=\"text-[#333333]/60 text-[13px] mt-4\">No spam. We&#x27;ll send you the report link and nothing else.</p></div></div></main><footer class=\"bg-[#0a1926]\"><div class=\"max-w-[1540px] mx-auto px-[105px] max-md:px-6 py-16\"><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-4 gap-12\"><div><img alt=\"Altimi\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"112\" height=\"28\" decoding=\"async\" data-nimg=\"1\" class=\"h-7 w-auto mb-6\" style=\"color:transparent\" srcSet=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-altimi-white.png&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 1x, /_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-altimi-white.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 2x\" src=\"/_next/image?url=%2Fimages%2Flogo-altimi-white.png&amp;w=256&amp;q=75\"/><p class=\"text-white/60 text-[14px] leading-[1.6] mb-4\">AI-powered system modernization for engineering leaders.</p><span class=\"font-mono text-[12px] uppercase tracking-[0.65px] text-white/60 bg-white/5 px-3 py-1 rounded\">ISO 27001 Certified</span></div><div><p class=\"font-mono text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.65px] text-white/60 mb-4\">Services</p><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-[15px] text-white/80\"><li><a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/jacek-podoba\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Discovery Sprint</a></li><li><a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/jacek-podoba\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Frontend Modernization</a></li><li><a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/jacek-podoba\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Backend Refactoring</a></li><li><a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/jacek-podoba\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Full Platform Modernization</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-mono text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.65px] text-white/60 mb-4\">Company</p><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-[15px] text-white/80\"><li><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">About Altimi</a></li><li><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Case Studies</a></li><li><a href=\"/resources\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Resources</a></li><li><a href=\"/privacy\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Privacy Policy</a></li><li><a href=\"#\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Terms</a></li></ul></div><div><p class=\"font-mono text-[13px] uppercase tracking-[0.65px] text-white/60 mb-4\">Contact</p><ul class=\"space-y-3 text-[15px] text-white/80\"><li><a href=\"https://meetings.hubspot.com/jacek-podoba\" class=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Get in touch</a></li></ul></div></div><div class=\"h-[2px] w-full mt-12 mb-8\" style=\"background-image:repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 0px, rgba(255,255,255,0.4) 5px, transparent 5px, transparent 12px)\"></div><p class=\"text-white/60 text-[14px] text-center\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Altimi. All rights reserved.</p></div></footer><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-0cc30f5d22cae38b.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[6943,[\\\"814\\\",\\\"static/chunks/814-9c5994eabc7467f2.js\\\",\\\"177\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/layout-3bfa2e48ad2203b4.js\\\"],\\\"TRPCReactProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[5389,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[7609,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[6855,[],\\\"ClientPageRoot\\\"]\\n6:I[2793,[\\\"201\\\",\\\"static/chunks/201-563e3800e322e1bb.js\\\",\\\"64\\\",\\\"static/chunks/64-6b869f8fe5c65808